PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FThey are also questioning whether they
OL,7,Fwere given the correct remains of
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,10,FThey are meeting for the first time -
OL,11,Fbound by a tragedy which unfolded in
OL,12,Fless than a minute and has left them
OL,13,Fwith questions that still haunt them.
OL,15,FITV News met Zunairah Master, Miten
OL,16,FPatel, Nick Meek, Nimmi Rajput, Chirag
OL,17,FPatel, Jay Mervana and Anisha Patel `
OL,18,Fwho between them lost mothers, fathers
OL,19,Fand brothers when Air India Flight 171
OL,20,Fcrashed seconds after take-off from
OL,21,FAhmedabad on 12th June 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FSome have never spoken publicly about
OL,7,Ftheir experiences before.
OL,9,FAlongside grief, there was deep
OL,10,Ffrustration and anger over what
OL,11,Ffamilies say was a lack of support
OL,12,Ffrom the British government.
OL,14,FNick Meek lost his brother Jamie, who
OL,15,Fhad been returning to the UK with his
OL,16,Fhusband.JNick describes the days after
OL,17,Fthe crash as filled with "complete
OL,18,Funcertainty".
OL,26,@yD@ZOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,F"There was a complete lack of
OL,7,Fcommunication and empathy," he said.
OL,8,F"You felt completely lost and you
OL,9,Fdon't know where to turn."
OL,11,FWhen asked whether he felt failed by
OL,12,Fthe British government, "100%." he
OL,13,Freplied.
OL,15,FMany of the families we spoke to
OL,16,Frushed immediately to India from the
OL,17,FUK after the crash.
OL,19,FThey described chaotic scenes and said
OL,20,Fthey received little information or
OL,21,Fguidance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@[O]tD@YOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
