PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FMany said they needed help navigating
OL,7,Fthe bureaucracy of identifying loved
OL,8,Fones at the hospital in India, instead
OL,9,Fthey say they felt abandoned by the UK
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FChirag Patel says his family received
OL,13,Falmost no help after registering with
OL,14,Fthe Foreign Office.
OL,16,F"There was no phone call," he
OL,17,Fsaid."They said, 'we're overwhelmed'.
OL,18,FThey were just like deer in
OL,19,Fheadlights."
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@ZO]yD@FOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FZunairah Master, who lost her 31 year
OL,7,Fold brother, Mohammed Adnan Master
OL,8,Fsaid: "The way were dealt with was
OL,9,Fjust atrocious. We had no support from
OL,10,Fthe (UK) government...my dad called
OL,11,Fthe British Embassy and they were of
OL,12,Fno help."
OL,14,FFamilies say they have since written
OL,15,Fto two successive Foreign Secretaries
OL,16,Frequesting meetings, but they have
OL,17,Fbeen ignored.
OL,19,FChirag questions whether the response
OL,20,Fwould have been different if the crash
OL,21,Fhad happened closer to home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,F"If this was a British tourist flight
OL,7,Fto one of the popular destinations, to
OL,8,Fthe Canaries (or) let's say to Greece,
OL,9,F"would there be more attention?," he
OL,10,Fasked. "Would they care?"
OL,12,FNick added: "It feels like they don't
OL,13,Fcare, because it never happened on
OL,14,Ftheir shores. But what they've got to
OL,15,Fremember is over 50 British taxpayers
OL,16,Fdied on that aeroplane and it's up to
OL,17,Fthem to help us and to assist us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
