CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FIn a statement to ITV News, a
OL,7,Fgovernment spokesperson said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with all the families
OL,9,Fand loved ones of the victims in this
OL,10,Ftragic accident.
OL,12,F"The Foreign Office continues to
OL,13,Fprovide support, including dedicated
OL,14,Fconsular caseworkers to each family
OL,15,Fwho requests our support and remain in
OL,16,Fcontact with the Indian authorities."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
