PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FOne of the most distressing themes to
OL,7,Femerge was uncertainty over whether
OL,8,Fsome of the families have been given
OL,9,Fthe correct remains of their loved
OL,10,Fones.
OL,12,FMany travelled to India to provide DNA
OL,13,Fsamples so victims could be identified
OL,14,Fand funerals could take place.
OL,16,FSome say they are still unsure whether
OL,17,Fthe person they laid to rest was truly
OL,18,Fthe person they lost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FChirag Patel, who lost his mother
OL,7,FManju Patel, said he cannot say with
OL,8,Fcertainty that the remains he cremated
OL,9,Fwere hers.
OL,11,F"Do you believe that you cremated your
OL,12,Fmum?," we asked him.
OL,14,F"Sadly, I cannot be 100% sure," he
OL,15,Freplied.
OL,17,F"There could be a chance it wasn't
OL,18,Fbecause I didn't repatriate (her body
OL,19,Fto the UK)."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FFor Miten Patel, who lost both his
OL,7,Fparents, Ashok and Shobhna, the
OL,8,Funcertainty became even more
OL,9,Fdistressing after the remains returned
OL,10,Fto the UK were examined.
OL,12,FWhen a UK coroner inspected one of the
OL,13,Fcaskets after it was repatriated,
OL,14,FMiten was told that his mother's
OL,15,Fremains had been mixed with someone
OL,16,Felse's.
OL,18,FIn India, he says he had never been
OL,19,Fallowed to check.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,F"Every single one of us when we were
OL,7,Fon the ground, you didn't know who you
OL,8,Fwere taking back," he recalled.
OL,10,F"We weren't allowed to see anything.
OL,11,FWe weren't allowed to physically
OL,12,Fidentify anything ourselves...And
OL,13,Funtil (we) came back to the UK and the
OL,14,Fcoroner opened the investigation,
OL,15,Fthat's when we knew that ok, we will
OL,16,Ffind out that this is mum and dad."
OL,18,FThe discovery has left him questioning
OL,19,Fwhat happened in the identification
OL,20,Fprocess.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FJay Mervana, who lost his father,
OL,7,Fdescribed a similar experience.
OL,9,F"We don't know if the full body was
OL,10,Fthere, if there was anything missing,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"We've just had to accept what they've
OL,14,Fgiven us."
OL,16,FHe says police remained present during
OL,17,Ffuneral rituals in India, ensuring the
OL,18,Fcoffins were not opened.
OL,20,F"That was confirmation we weren't
OL,21,Fgoing to open them."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@fO]uD@AOUvD@JO]|D@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
