PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FFor some families, those doubts have
OL,7,Fonly grown with time.
OL,9,FAnisha Patel whose father, Nilkanth
OL,10,Fdied in the crash, said: "We just had
OL,11,Fhis name on the box and that's it. And
OL,12,Fyou just take that as face value
OL,13,Fbecause you can't open it and double
OL,14,Fcheck anything."
OL,16,FZunairah said she just wanted her
OL,17,Fbrother's body back so her family
OL,18,Fcould bury him quickly, in accordance
OL,19,Fwith Islam, but it took "so long".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,F"You could smell it. You could smell
OL,7,Fthe stench of death," she said.
OL,9,FThe families say their experience was
OL,10,Fmade even worse because of a lack of
OL,11,Fsupport from the British government.
OL,13,FThey believe the Foreign Office should
OL,14,Fnow help them find answers about their
OL,15,Floved ones remains and about the cause
OL,16,Fcrash.
OL,18,FWhen we asked them if they felt the
OL,19,Fgovernment was advocating on their
OL,20,Fbehalf, several answered immediately:
OL,21,F"No, not at all."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FFor Anisha Patel the uncertainty has
OL,7,Fmade it impossible to move forward.
OL,9,FHer father Nilkanth had survived
OL,10,Fcancer before his sudden death in the
OL,11,Fcrash came as a devastating shock.
OL,13,FLike many of the families, she says
OL,14,Fthe same questions keep returning.
OL,16,F"How did it happen? Why did it happen?"
OL,18,FUntil they know, many say they are
OL,19,Funable to grieve properly.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,FBecause for these families, the crash
OL,7,Fwas over in seconds.
OL,9,FBut the search for answers is far from
OL,10,Fover.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Air India said:
OL,13,F"Families have been going through
OL,14,Funimaginable grief since this tragedy
OL,15,Fand our responsibility to support and
OL,16,Fcare for them remains our absolute
OL,17,Fpriority.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773245484
OL,3,CAir India crash families come together
OL,4,Cfor the first time, demanding answers
OL,6,F"We have remained in close and regular
OL,7,Fcontact with the families over the
OL,8,Flast nine months, offering our full
OL,9,Fsupport during this difficult time,
OL,10,Feither directly or through their legal
OL,11,Frepresentatives where they have chosen
OL,12,Fthis route, to ensure they are kept
OL,13,Finformed of any and all developments.
OL,15,F"We wholeheartedly understand that
OL,16,Fmonetary compensation could never make
OL,17,Fup for the loss of a loved one and are
OL,18,Fcommitted to doing everything to
OL,19,Fsupport every single impacted family
OL,20,Fas they navigate this difficult time."
OL,26,@|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
